# Program

The Master 1 year consists of two semesters and allows you to earn 60 ECTS (European Credits Transfer System).
 
Each semester consists of core and optional modules. Each student must complete a Personal Project in one of the partner institutions ([I3S](http://www.i3s.unice.fr/) or [INRIA](http://www.inria.fr/)) for a total of 6 ECTS credits (equivalent to around 120 hrs fo work). 

In addition, three courses Introduction to Research 1 & 2 and Scientific Writing aim at giving students a first experience in Research.

